You know you want a piece of this.

17:53.840 --> 17:55.808
Pablo,
believe it or not,

17:55.960 --> 17:58.008
the rude middle-aged man
you brought

17:58.160 --> 18:00.527
is kinda ruining
my mom time.

18:00.720 --> 18:02.927
( Buzzing )

18:03.080 --> 18:05.128
Ash, you're wrong,
I'm right.

18:05.280 --> 18:07.487
Lay off.
That's her real mom.

18:09.880 --> 18:12.201
Well, can we get back to dinner

18:12.400 --> 18:15.483
or, um, did you have
some more questions for me?

18:15.640 --> 18:16.971
Seriously.

18:18.240 --> 18:20.083
