18:39.520 --> 18:41.488
Ash!

18:45.640 --> 18:47.005
( Gasps )

18:48.160 --> 18:50.640
Oh, good. I was starting
to feel like a real dick.

18:50.800 --> 18:51.801
H-honey?

18:51.960 --> 18:53.166
(growling )

18:53.360 --> 18:55.408
