( Thunder crashing )

20:52.280 --> 20:54.487
Kelly, please.

20:54.640 --> 20:57.883
( Sobbing )
Please help me.

20:58.040 --> 21:02.011
L-I don't know
what's going on.

21:02.160 --> 21:04.049
You...

21:04.240 --> 21:05.446
you killed Dad.

21:05.600 --> 21:06.965
Oh, no.
( sobbing )

21:07.160 --> 21:08.571
Oh, God.

21:11.760 --> 21:15.810
L-I blacked out.
I...

21:16.000 --> 21:19.607
Oh, please.
I think you can--

21:19.760 --> 21:22.081
I think you can
help me beat it.

21:22.240 --> 21:24.288
I will.
I will, Mommy.

21:24.440 --> 21:26.841
I'll help you,
I'll help you.

21:27.000 --> 21:28.331
( Crashes )

21:29.680 --> 21:31.808
You left dinner
before Daddy excused you.

21:31.960 --> 21:35.328
No, no, wait. Wait, look.
She's fine, she's fine.

21:35.520 --> 21:37.045
She's fighting it.
We can save her.

21:37.200 --> 21:38.884
It's too late for saving.
Back off.

21:39.040 --> 21:41.884
- No, no.
- Baby, baby, it's okay.

21:42.040 --> 21:44.008
- No.
- Come here, come here.

21:44.160 --> 21:46.527
Baby...

21:46.680 --> 21:48.205
