21:50.720 --> 21:53.087
I drove up that bridge
on purpose...

21:54.760 --> 21:57.331
( low voice )
...to get away from you.

21:57.480 --> 21:59.687
( Screaming )

22:04.280 --> 22:06.931
Now the three of you
will perish together.

22:07.080 --> 22:08.491
